# Skill: verify-kit-eval

## When to use
- User asks to run evals or compare two runs.
- Before merging a prompt change.

## Status (Phase 3 stub)
The eval body is implemented in Phase 5. In Phase 3, `verify-kit eval run` and
`verify-kit eval compare` return `{"status": "not_implemented", "available_in_phase": 5}`.
When that JSON appears, surface the message to the user — do not silently
proceed.

## Future invocation (Phase 5)
- `just eval` runs Promptfoo against `eval/datasets/golden.jsonl`.
- `verify-kit eval compare run-a run-b` diffs two stored runs.
